---
---
<section class="relative py-32 mt-20 overflow-hidden kinetic-slant-reverse">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#006b1b]">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="flex gap-4 rotate-12 -mt-40">
                <div class="w-20 h-[1000px] bg-[#fdd835]"></div>
                <div class="w-20 h-[1000px] bg-[#fdd835]"></div>
                <div class="w-20 h-[1000px] bg-[#fdd835]"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 px-8 md:px-24 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-12">
        <div class="max-w-2xl">
            <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-headline font-black text-[#d1ffc8] uppercase italic tracking-tighter leading-none">
                Tu Legado Empieza <br/> <span class="text-[#fdd835]">En La Pista</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-[#9bfc96] font-medium">
                Únete a la Liga de Atletismo del Chocó. Contamos con entrenadores certificados, infraestructura en desarrollo y el espíritu indomable del Pacífico.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 w-full md:w-auto">
            <button class="bg-white text-[#006b1b] px-12 py-5 font-headline font-black uppercase tracking-tight text-xl transition-all hover:bg-[#fdd835] hover:text-[#5b4b00]" style="clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 92% 100%, 0 100%);">
                Afíliate Hoy
            </button>
            <p class="text-[#d1ffc8] text-center md:text-left text-sm opacity-80 italic">Cupos abiertos para semilleros y clubes regionales.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
